Add the `rich_rust` crate as an optional dependency with proper feature flags for conditional compilation.

## Changes to Cargo.toml
```toml
[dependencies]
# Terminal output (keep existing for fallback)
colored = "2.1"
indicatif = "0.17"
console = "0.15"

# Rich terminal output (optional)
rich_rust = { version = "0.1", optional = true, features = ["full"] }

